165
00:10:37,110 --> 00:10:39,200
You still can regret now.

166
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:40,640
Don't estimate me.

167
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:44,400
I'm telling you, I, Huang Weijie,

168
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,710
will be a hero.

